:"2017-09-03T12:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用番舊個個好過<br />\n新版第一次上我以為入撚左app版youtube<br />\n好似用緊app咁<br />\n好不爽</blockquote><br />\n但係有dark mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f40fd041be483d068043f7f2afcfe7f0719aadc","tid":385533,"uid":128089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T21:58:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我幾日前已經變咗咁，呢D更新每次都只會愈來愈差。<br />\n無論YOUTUBE, FACEBOOK, MICROSOFT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW, 都唔知有時D更新更來做乜，愈整愈差...</blockquote><br />\n我幾鍾意新依個喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然今次呢個無太大的問題，但一樣有唔方便的地方。<br />\n平時我睇片會一次過開晒咁多條係TAB度，然後遂條遂條睇<br />\n一開就即刻PAUSE等佢自己LOAD，但依家已經唔可以，要等佢LOAD一陣。<br />\n仲有好多架，其實。每次更新都唔見有咩好到，差咗就一定有，係多定少。<br />\n<br />\nFACEBOOK就更甚，每次更新好似倒退十年一樣。"},{"pid":"688c32b8b85c1a991c2f6b9a98bcff17d407e2c4","tid":385533,"uid":130349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T22:23:57.000Z","msg":"好撚唔好用啵 師兄"},{"pid":"ff9eeb9a076a5cf51a53c8c778b44e0ba89b8ee3","tid":385533,"uid":105838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T23:58:22.000Z","msg":"Dark mode 邊到轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4584e0d5f2a5f041f1781d611a62e9254e258061","tid":385533,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T02:11:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Dark mode 邊到轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/101120_4858f62f57c669a69810eba83147b4fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F101120_4858f62f57c669a69810eba83147b4fc.jpg&h=ef6b60ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係咁難搵咩"},{"pid":"f102d4cf156ad8c611c405a6a0aa7ddef367c0e8","tid":385533,"uid":1249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T02:12:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我幾日前已經變咗咁，呢D更新每次都只會愈來愈差。<br />\n無論YOUTUBE, FACEBOOK, MICROSOFT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW, 都唔知有時D更新更來做乜，愈整愈差...</blockquote><br />\n我幾鍾意新依個喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然今次呢個無太大的問題，但一樣有唔方便的地方。<br />\n平時我睇片會一次過開晒咁多條係TAB度，然後遂條遂條睇<br />\n一開就即刻PAUSE等佢自己LOAD，但依家已經唔可以，要等佢LOAD一陣。<br />\n仲有好多架，其實。每次更新都唔見有咩好到，差咗就一定有，係多定少。<br />\n<br />\nFACEBOOK就更甚，每次更新好似倒退十年一樣。</blockquote><br />\n我無依個習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對我無影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b20e6d10ae658b06bf229b54cb6ddf5dd116011","tid":385533,"uid":116684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T02:15:48.000Z","msg":"舊版好多時禁一下就做到既功能, 新版要禁幾下先去到, 例如改我video 既topic 同information 錦, 仲有唔知點解感覺上新版比舊版慢"},{"pid":"ab474d532668c288c9e154eb6d267bfbadfa4b7e","tid":385533,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊版好多時禁一下就做到既功能, 新版要禁幾下先去到, 例如改我video 既topic 同information 錦, 仲有唔知點解感覺上新版比舊版慢</blockquote><br />\n呢個係所有更新都會有的問題，係多定少，我冇讀過IT唔知個原理係點，<br />\n明明最早期係一撳就可以LOAD到，依家懶係靚懶係華麗，想打少少野都要LOAD成秒。<br />\n<br />\n但今次YOUTUBE有樣野好咗，就係留COMMENT果個BAR上一版係撳幾次先打到字，更新咗之後終於一撳就可以打字。"},{"pid":"83c07e791195a8f881b3b26f2d07b8c90af689f0","tid":385533,"uid":4502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:30:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又靚左又好用左喎 有dark mode都夠啦 點解要轉返舊?</blockquote><br />\n我係想用新喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://Youtube.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FYoutube.com&d=WIzY31M6lTuMVoQXvoSpLgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=f8c6abee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Youtube.com</a>之後/new<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720ed4f5e1fdd21b1077a38f5b70cc1ab70c3aa3","tid":385533,"uid":58097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:19:28.000Z","msg":"係咪冇咗loop條片個掣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f0d959749e69ca1bebf4693a7eb080c0162386","tid":385533,"uid":64813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:22:00.000Z","msg":"識野呀睇BOB叔 佢D郵輪片好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2af7f493b29ae9f39633763d55639919659f9d4","tid":385533,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:27:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪冇咗loop條片個掣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係"}]}